snippet.title: Fluidified
snippet.description:
The finest in deep, chilled and atmospheric electronic music. Genres include chillout, downtempo, ambient, future garage and others.

Uses for the music include relaxation, studying, concentration, stress relief, mindfulness, meditation, sleeping, etc.

Music on the channel may only be used with the artists' permission, links to their pages can be found in the descriptions.

Submissions, general inquiries: contact(at)fluidified.com
